assassin
Block;;1;Periodically reduces the damage received from Hero Basic Attacks by 50%. Stores up to 2 charges.
Greater Cleave;;1;Increases the radius of Cleave by 33%.
Rapid Displacement;;1;Reduces the cooldown of Blink by 1.5 seconds.
Regeneration Master;;1;Every 3 Regeneration Globes gathered grants an extra +4 Health per second, permanently.
Seasoned Marksman;;1;For every 6 enemy Minion or Mercenary kills near your Hero, gain 1 Basic Attack damage. Hero Takedowns count as 2 Minion kills.
Focused Attack;;4;Every 10 seconds, your next Basic Attack deals 50% additional damage. Basic Attacks reduce this cooldown by 1 second.
Vampiric Assault;;4;Basic Attacks heal for 15% of the damage dealt.
Gathering Power;;4;Passively grants 8% Ability Power. Each Hero takedown grants a bonus 2% Ability Power, up to 12%. This bonus Ability Power is lost upon death.
Sustained Anomaly;;4;The Singularity Spike explodes for area damage and slows, regardless if it hits a target or not.
Vorpal Blade;;4;Activate to teleport to the last non-structure target you attacked within 3 seconds. 15 second cooldown.
Follow Through;;7;After using an ability, your next Basic Attack deals 25% additional damage.
Rending Cleave;;7;Cleave deals an additional 50% damage over 5 seconds.
Shadow Spike;;7;No longer decloak when using Singularity Spike. Range increased by 20%.
First Aid;;7;Activate to heal 11.07% of your max Health over 6 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Searing Attacks;;7;Activate to increase Basic Attack damage by 50% for 5 seconds. Each attack costs 15 Mana. 25s cooldown.
Shadow Assault;;10;Your Basic Attacks cause you to charge at enemies and have +20% Attack Speed. Lasts for 6 seconds. 100s cooldown.
Void Prison;;10;Trap ALL targets for 5 seconds, making them become invulnerable. You are not affected. 100s cooldown.
Giant Killer;;13;Basic Attacks against enemy Heroes deal bonus damage equal to 1.5% of the Hero's max Health.
Burning Rage;;13;Deal 10 damage per second to nearby enemies.
Wormhole;;13;For 3 seconds, you can activate Blink again to return to the point where it was cast from.
Assassin's Blade (Trait);;13;Gain 25% Attack Damage for 5 seconds when breaking cloak. 10% increased Movement Speed while cloaked.
Spell Shield;;13;Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce all Ability Damage taken by 50% for 2 seconds. Can only trigger once every 30 seconds.
Executioner;;16;Basic Attacks deal 40% more damage against slowed, rooted, or stunned targets.
Void Slash;;16;Cleave deals 30% increased damage if used while cloaked.
Double Bombs;;16;After you cast Singularity Spike, you can cast a second one for free within 3 seconds.
Stoneskin;;16;Activate to gain 30% of your Max Health as Shields for 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Berserk;;16;Activate to increase your Attack Speed by 40% and Movement Speed by 10% for 4 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Fury of the Storm;;20;Basic Attacks bounce twice to nearby enemies for 50% damage.
Bolt of the Storm;;20;Activate to teleport to a nearby location. 40s cooldown.
Nerazim Fury;;20;Shadow Assault grants 30% Life Steal, and the duration is increased by 50%.
Protective Prison;;20;Allies are also no longer affected by Void Prison.